🩺 HealthCard
"A Django-based web application for managing and verifying digital health cards."
📊 Smart healthcare management with authentication & medicine tracking.

📸 Screenshots
Homepage	Medicine Details	Admin Dashboard	Add Medicine

🔧 Features
👤 User Registration/Login

🧾 Digital Health Card Verification

💊 Medicine Inventory & Sales Tracking

🛡️ Admin Dashboard

📁 SQLite Database Integration

🚀 Tech Stack
Python & Django

HTML/CSS

Bootstrap

SQLite

JavaScript

HealthCard/
│
├── health/               # Django app
├── HealthCard/           # Project config
├── media/                # Uploaded files
├── screenshots/          # UI images
├── db.sqlite3            # Database
├── manage.py             # Entrypoint
└── requirements.txt      # Dependencies

---

## 🚀 How to Run

```bash
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/YOUR-USERNAME/HealthCard.git
cd HealthCard

# Create virtual environment
python -m venv env
env\Scripts\activate  # On Windows

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Run migrations
python manage.py migrate

# Start the server
python manage.py runserver

